The Logomattic Portlet is an improvement of the built-in GateIn Logo Portlet: it allows to upload a logo in Java Content Repository (JCR).

The Logomattic Portlet is built using the Chromattic mapping framework to JCR and is also a simple application to demonstrate easy JCR persistence with Chromattic.

To install the Portlet you can watch this tutorial : http://vimeo.com/15590563
